data.description: This exceptional home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and an open floor plan.  As you enter the front door, you will find a bedroom and bathroom on the main floor.  Walking towards the rear of the home you'll find a spacious living room with an open concept layout that allows for a seamless flow between the living room, kitchen and dining area, making it perfect for entertaining and spending time with family. The kitchen features modern stainless appliances, solid surface countertops, tile backsplash and a kitchen island, providing functionality and a central gathering spot.  Plus, from the kitchen, you have a view of the backyard that offers space for outdoor activities and relaxation.  Heading to the second floor, you are greeted with an upstairs bonus room.  this additional space can serve as a home office, entertainment area and much more...just use your imagination.  Also, on the second floor, there are 2 bedrooms and another bathroom with the added bonus of having the laundry room upstairs near the bedrooms!  The master suite offers a spacious bedroom area, providing a comfortable and private retreat.  Connected to the master bedroom, the master bath features a luxurious shower and double sinks.  Additionally, the master suite includes a generously sized closet, offering plenty of storage space.  Wesbridge is a gated community in the heart of Wesley   Chapel with pool/play area, playground, dog park, covered events venue with bathrooms & outdoor showers.  Conveniently located close to Boyette Farm, Wesley Chapel District Park, newly opened I-75 Overpass access and walking distance to Wesley Chapel Elementary, Thomas Weightman MS and Wesley Chapel HS.
